{"tid":391353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得laiza好靚","createTime":"2017-09-07T16:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T17:19:39.000Z","uid":76831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"62624ea8bb019eb98e4e1e88cea09ca8be48e9b7","tid":391353,"uid":76831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/005215_485529492d09052637e0cbaf3e735952.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F005215_485529492d09052637e0cbaf3e735952.jpg&h=de4b71ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/005310_ee034fec33e188ee6b8b32700d743ba3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F005310_ee034fec33e188ee6b8b32700d743ba3.jpg&h=b73418ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/005324_31e0c064f148a210b3e15a40db8a96ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F005324_31e0c064f148a210b3e15a40db8a96ba.jpg&h=91551f53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係好靚好有氣質<br />\n好靚好靚好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但成日係story 放啲隻貓摸佢胸既相<br />\n今次仲要激凸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/005455_6d86828e16ec00bbf38e9265c0162f3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F005455_6d86828e16ec00bbf38e9265c0162f3e.jpg&h=e920fb0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/005517_15c33dcc46eeaa3ea9fc37e258aff7d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F005517_15c33dcc46eeaa3ea9fc37e258aff7d9.jpg&h=b01951d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時係走文青氣質小清新路線<br />\n但story 就咁<br />\n算唔算外表斯文 內裡open<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d74bc44f4bb9fa04d24e0cbbdb666d66d37351","tid":391353,"uid":76831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}